column4: Exact match, including case

contains parenthesis: first word with incorrect lowercase

contains parenthesis: both words correct case and a parenthesis

Exact match all words (including case)
All words match, but all wrong lowercase

Hidden category: both words, correct case. Should not match.

see discussion starting at https://github.com/commons-app/apps-android-commons/issues/3179#issuecomment-607259657
matches the middle of the category, all case correct
matches the middle of the category, all case incorrect lowercase

Category without Category:* page: incorrect lowercase 3.5 words

Category without Category:* page: starts with quote marks: incorrect lowercase first word, but has quotes
